item.title: Windows Phone 7: The AnandTech Guide
item.author: youremail@domain.com (Some Person)
item.description: Recapitulation Microsoft MIX 2010 has drawn to a close, and with it comes our concluding wrap-up of everything that there is to discuss about Windows Phone 7 Series (henceforth WP7S).
